{"title":"孩子们","authors":["王文福"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":6,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王文福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客人抱起我的孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵笑声朗朗："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嘿！象秤砣一样！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑子里猛地一亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，我们的一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不都是因为孩子们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才有了准确的重量？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我们的欢乐和忧伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的汗水和遐想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有我们手腕上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那表针嚓嚓地奔忙……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}